Title: Dilema
Director: Adilla Dimitri, Robby Ertanto, Rinaldy Puspoyo, Robert Ronny
Writer: Adilla Dimitri, Robby Ertanto, Wulan Guritno, Rinaldy Puspoyo, Robert Ronny
Actors: Kenes Andari, Abimana Aryasatya, Ario Bayu, Rangga Djoned
Plot: Dilemma is an omnibus film, five stories that depict dark side of Jakarta's underbelly. Jakarta's underground world that seldom to talk about, and forgotten by most of the people.
